snippet.title: Kenya CitizenTV
snippet.description:
CITIZEN TV is the No.1 TV station commanding a total reach of 90% and over 12 years in existence as pioneer brand for RMS Footprint with largest coverage and reach (country wide) covers all socioeconomic grouping speaks to all ages all gender.

Citizen TV is in KAMPALA & ZAMBIA on a free to air signal and on DSTV channel 146 in UG, TZ, DRC, RWANDA, BURUNDI & SOUTH SUDAN.

 Programming: NEWS, LOCAL SHOWS, TELENOVELAS, AFROSINEMA, MUSIC & REALITY SHOWS
